{"tid":1778441,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"華爾街日報：監警會國際專家組請辭","createTime":"2019-12-11T03:18:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T04:51:20.000Z","uid":257272,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"16de43ff6c20195598cb691a8661f476dae2160d","tid":1778441,"uid":257272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:18:40.000Z","msg":"華爾街日報：監警會國際專家組請辭<br />\n<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwodddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=5bef074c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a> 新聞<br />\n<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwodddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=5bef074c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a> 新聞 <br />\n2019年12月11日 上午8:54<br />\n留言<br />\n<br />\n華爾街日報：監警會國際專家組請辭<br />\n更多<br />\n【Now新聞台】監警會早前聘請五名海外專家，協助監警會審視近日示威活動中的警務工作及程序，《華爾街日報》報道，國際專家組決定請辭。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，國際專家組認為，監警會缺乏足夠權力完成調查，以滿足香港市民的期望，專家組無法與監警會協調出能有效支持研究報告的機制，決定請辭。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述小組成員斯托特指，小組建議監警會應有權力，辨認及保護警隊內外的證人，監警會要達至這個基本要求，才能有效化解香港目前的危機。<br />\n<br />\n專家組認為，在未清楚政府是否支持成立獨立調查委員會下，一個對香港人具備公信力的監警會報告至為重要；監警會暫時未回應有關報道。<br />\n<br />\n監警會是在今年九月初公布聘用五名國際專家，協助監警會審視近日示威活動中的警務工作及程序。監警會主席梁定邦早前接受內地媒體訪問時指，專家組對香港情況的了解不全面，已向專家組說明監警會必須按目前的法律辦事。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n#要聞<br />\n<br />\n割席啦. 不過係同你地班黑犬割席呀!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8902f1d0a25b6793fe0949236bd93fc45ed83e1","tid":1778441,"uid":37058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:19:25.000Z","msg":"專家都同暴力割席<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9feada4bbbfd4faff39f506adf7a6c7ca3130187","tid":1778441,"uid":20870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:21:02.000Z","msg":"人地副主席話係階段性完成工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係on9"},{"pid":"d495b93868bd6457effa023d38541c091ffd0541","tid":1778441,"uid":257272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:25:06.000Z","msg":"監警會:國際專家唔夠專業, 我地會轉聘內地專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba98205f538c5417f56594928b3a67723d3b1335","tid":1778441,"uid":31200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:42:48.000Z","msg":"以為好似大陸咁比錢請專家就任你點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"048a0c1b3592cbb172db5fcf3937669ebd824c2a","tid":1778441,"uid":69746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:44:07.000Z","msg":"專家：你個野都無用嘅"},{"pid":"c81a006a0b885cbf41a5c4deb5853a223a9bb6e1","tid":1778441,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T04:51:20.000Z","msg":"sorry p牌仔借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n男銷售員 6 月涉推跌六旬男子致死被控謀殺　控方近半年仍未能確定死因<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776775\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776775</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}